  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nCurrently we get connected peers by looping through all peers in the peer store and check if we have any connections for that peer and we have a performance issue with it.\r\nIn my medalla libp2p peer store, I got more than 800 peers.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nWe should be able to get that directly from the connection manager using its `connections` map https://github.com/libp2p/js-libp2p/blob/v0.30.0/src/connection-manager/index.js#L92\r\n",
